CHANGE
  Change your country's password or other settings.

SYNTAX
  change <setting> <value>
  chan   <setting> <value>

DESCRIPTION
  Modifies account settings for your country.

  Settings:
    password <new-password>   change your login password
    name     <new-name>       change your country's display name

  Passwords are stored securely (bcrypt hashed).  Choose a password
  other players won't guess — country names are public.

EXAMPLE
  change password hunter2   set new password
  change name Atlantis      rename your country

SEE ALSO
  nation  add
